@page "/compare"
@inherits PageCore<Compare>

<SeoMeta Title="Compare" Description="..." Url="/compare" Index="true"></SeoMeta>
<NewPageSection IsPageHeader="true" Image="icon/icon-71.png" Title="Compare" Description="..." CustomBodyClass="mb-12"></NewPageSection>

<NewPageSection Title="Introduction / Overview">
    <BodyFragment>
        O que mostrar:

        Contextualizar a diferença entre serviços de encontros e matchmaking.
        Frase exemplo: “Not all platforms for meeting people are created equal. Here’s how Modern Matchmaker compares to traditional approaches.”
    </BodyFragment>
</NewPageSection>

<NewPageSection Title="Comparison Table / Visual">
    <BodyFragment>
        Colunas:

        Feature / Aspect	Dating Apps	Traditional Matchmaking	Modern Matchmaker

        Linhas / Features sugeridas:

        Matching approach (swipe vs curated vs algorithm + human)
        Quality of matches (quantity-focused vs selective vs quality-driven)
        Personalization (low vs high vs high + data-driven)
        Time investment required (high vs high vs low-medium)
        Global vs local reach
        Transparency / explanation of score
        Safety / verification
        Cost model (subscription, per-introduction, tokenized, etc.)

        Visual suggestion: Pode ser uma tabela colorida, ícones ou barras comparativas.
    </BodyFragment>
</NewPageSection>

<NewPageSection Title="Detailed Breakdown">
    <BodyFragment>
        O que mostrar:

        Dating Apps: rápido, massivo, superficial, baseado em fotos e swipes.
        Traditional Matchmaking: muito personalizado, caro, limitado geograficamente, baseado em consultoria humana.
        Modern Matchmaker: algoritmo + curadoria humana, global, mais acessível, foco em compatibilidade e intenção real.
    </BodyFragment>
</NewPageSection>

<NewPageSection Title="Why Modern Matchmaker is Different">
    <BodyFragment>
        O que mostrar:

        Reforçar diferenciais do seu serviço:
        Alcance global
        Algoritmo + curadoria
        Compatibilidade baseada em dados e intenções reais
        Transparência e segurança
        Pode usar bullets ou ícones para visual.
    </BodyFragment>
</NewPageSection>

<NewPageSection Title="Call to Action">
    <BodyFragment>
        O que mostrar:

        Incentivo suave: “Discover the difference for yourself – create your profile today.”
        Botão de cadastro discreto.
    </BodyFragment>
</NewPageSection>

<FloatingButton Template="Template.Back"></FloatingButton>

